      "value": "<p>&gt;@UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.class-features.Item.Z1V1TmTxPhgur7n1]{Melophile}</p>\n<p>When you use your song of the spheres connection power, affected allies gain resistance to a number of types of energy damage of your choice equal to half the level of the spell slot that you expended (minimum 1). If you spent a Resolve Point, affected allies gain resistance to a number of types of energy damage equal to half the level of the highest level of mystic spell that you can cast (minimum 1). Resistance granted by this connection power is equal to your mystic level and lasts for the duration of your song of the spheres.</p>"
